            "description": "<div data-page-id=\"Sk9KdrpfSodGVrxSspkl1j7bgJh\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<h3 class=\"heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-YR9pdiuYWovNvYxcYBXlNKu0gyg\">Questions 5-10</h3>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ZNTadfU9korz90xiWBblnJmogZf\">Which feature is related to each of the following areas of the world represented in the playground?</div>\n<div data-page-id=\"Sk9KdrpfSodGVrxSspkl1j7bgJh\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\">\n<div class=\" old-record-id-SQjDdfqhQojW9axtDu1l8GLug1c\" data-type=\"sheet\">\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100.055%;\" border=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><col style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><col style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><strong>A.&nbsp;</strong>ancient forts</p>\n<p><strong>D.&nbsp;</strong>jewels</p>\n<p><strong>G. </strong>music and film</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><strong>B.&nbsp;</strong>waterways</p>\n<p><strong>E.&nbsp;</strong>local animals</p>\n<p><strong>H. </strong>space travel</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><strong>C.&nbsp;</strong>ice and snow</p>\n<p><strong>F. </strong>mountains</p>\n<p><strong>I. </strong>volcanoes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
